Motivation:
1)Finding the next greater element for each element

2)Given an array and an integer k, find the maximum for each and every contiguous subarray of size k.

Example:
Input :
arr[] = {1, 2, 3, 1, 4, 5, 2, 3, 6}
k = 3
Output :
3 3 4 5 5 5 6

problem link:http://www.spoj.com/problems/ARRAYSUB/

Other Problems links:
http://codeforces.com/contest/5/problem/C
